<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>E-Vaulto | Secure Your Data</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-dark: #0b0f0c;
      --bg-card: #121816;
      --text-main: #e6e6e6;
      --text-muted: #9aa5a0;
      --accent: #22c55e;
      --accent-soft: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.25);
      --border: #1f2a25;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #16201b, #050706);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      color: var(--text-main);
      overflow-x: hidden;
      animation: pageFade 1.2s ease forwards;
    }

    /* PAGE FADE */
    @keyframes pageFade {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    /* CONTAINER */
    .container {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 70px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* LOGO */
    .logo {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      animation: glowPulse 2.5s infinite alternate;
    }

    .logo span {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-shadow: 0 0 18px var(--accent-soft);
    }

    @keyframes glowPulse {
      from {
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-soft);
      }
      to {
        text-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--accent);
      }
    }

    /* TEXT */
    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
      animation-delay: 0.3s;
      opacity: 0;
    }

    .subline {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 50px;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
      animation-delay: 0.6s;
      opacity: 0;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from {
        transform: translateY(25px);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    /* BUTTONS */
    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 25px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
      animation-delay: 0.9s;
      opacity: 0;
    }

    .btn {
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 38px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .btn::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: -100%;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(
        120deg,
        transparent,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2),
        transparent
      );
      transition: left 0.6s;
    }

    .btn:hover::before {
      left: 100%;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #04110a;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-soft);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 0 35px var(--accent);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--accent);
      border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #04110a;
      transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--accent);
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 35px 20px 45px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #060907;
      animation: slideUp 1s ease forwards;
      animation-delay: 1.2s;
      opacity: 0;
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
      from {
        transform: translateY(40px);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    .footer small {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .about-title {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .about-text {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #aeb8b2;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">E-<span>Vaulto</span></div>

    <p class="tagline">Secure your data. Own your privacy.</p>
    <p class="subline">
      Passwords • Game IDs • Expenses • Notes
    </p>

    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-secondary">Login</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="footer">
    <small>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> E-Vaulto. All rights reserved.</small>
    <p class="about-title">About E-Vaulto</p>
    <p class="about-text">
      E-Vaulto is your personal digital vault — built to securely manage passwords,
      game IDs, notes, and Track expenses with simplicity, encryption, and complete control.
    </p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
